{
  "stem": "6016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I watched [NON-ENGLISH], which I was satisfied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And winter time was the snow, which until today I liked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I like the snow, but I wouldn't like to live in a country where the snow is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I loved the mountains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the general activities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A little in the woods we had the close by to pick up blueberries, and little, I think, mushrooms too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was a little, it was a little variety.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nothing can compare to think of today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had cousins, and my aunts that lived not far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to bring the children to stay for the summer, which we were very fortunate to, to be able to treat them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same times, we gained too, because if we went to a farm to have some fresh milk, fresh, fresh cheeses, sour, sour yogurt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was real nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a real vacation time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And holidays, were very observant too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This I don't remember having them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think whether I even know about this word bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they went, maybe they had only in the temple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't recall any of the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we even had in our close by on our back yard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one part of the house, of the next door house, that it was like small steeple.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like they call it like a little house where the congregants got together and they were praying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the main synagogue was we had to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was close by, was in a walking distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish community was very nice, especially Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I used to go Saturday with my mother to visit someone.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
